---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import TextFormat from "lib/helpers/TextFormat";
---

<Layout title="The buildCAP: Get the Best">
   <section
      class="container relative mt-24 flex w-full max-w-[1700px] flex-col gap-16 overflow-x-hidden px-container-base pt-4 md:gap-[10rem] md:py-[4.5rem] md:pt-[4.5rem] lg:px-container-lg xl:px-container-xl"
   >
      <div
         class="relative flex w-full flex-col gap-[1.5rem] md:grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] md:gap-[2.75rem]"
      >
         <div class="flex flex-grow flex-col justify-center gap-6 2xl:gap-8">
            <h1
               class="max-w-[40rem] text-left text-[2rem] font-[600] leading-[130%] tracking-[0.02rem] text-secondary-2 transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out md:text-[4.4rem] md:leading-[5rem] md:tracking-[0.0225rem] lg:ml-[-0.2rem]"
            >
               <TextFormat
                  text={" Empowering Construction, Building Futures."}
                  keyword={"Construction"}
                  keywordClassName="text-primary-1 transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out"
               />
            </h1>

            <div class="mb-5 flex gap-4 md:mb-0 md:ml-[-6px]">
               <a href="/" class="rounded-lg">
                  <img
                     src="/svgs/tools/android.svg"
                     class="h-[3.2rem] w-[7rem] lg:h-[5.5rem] lg:w-[6rem]"
                  />
               </a>
               <a href="/" class="rounded-lg">
                  <img
                     src="/svgs/tools/ios.svg"
                     class="h-[3.2rem] w-[7rem] lg:h-[5.5rem] lg:w-[6rem]"
                  />
               </a>
            </div>
         </div>

         <section>
            <div
               class="relative flex h-full max-h-[45rem] min-h-[25.375rem] w-full flex-col items-end justify-between rounded-3xl lg:min-h-[30.375rem] 2xl:min-h-[40.375rem]"
               style={{
                  background: `linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)), url('/images/about/hero2.jpg')`,
                  backgroundSize: "cover",
                  backgroundPosition: "center",
               }}
            >
            </div>
         </section>
      </div>
      <div
         class="relative flex w-full flex-col-reverse gap-[1.5rem] md:grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] md:gap-[2.75rem]"
      >
         <section>
            <div
               class="relative flex h-full max-h-[45rem] min-h-[25.375rem] w-full flex-col items-end justify-between rounded-3xl lg:min-h-[30.375rem] 2xl:min-h-[40.375rem]"
               style={{
                  background: `linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)), url('/images/about/hero1.jpg')`,
                  backgroundSize: "cover",
                  backgroundPosition: "center",
               }}
            >
            </div>
         </section>
         <div class="flex flex-grow flex-col justify-center gap-6 2xl:gap-8">
            <p
               class="w-fit rounded-full bg-primary-1/5 p-4 px-6 text-lg font-[900] text-primary-1 md:p-4 md:px-8 md:text-2xl"
            >
               Our Mission
            </p>

            <p class="text-[1.18rem] leading-[2.4rem] tracking-[0.0225rem] text-gray-500">
               At buildCAP, we are committed to revolutionizing the construction industry by
               providing innovative financial solutions. Our mission is to bridge the gap between
               ambition and reality for subcontractors, enabling them to undertake and complete
               projects with confidence and efficiency. We understand the challenges of cash flow
               and financing in the construction sector, and we are here to provide a dependable
               lifeline.
            </p>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div
         class="relative flex w-full flex-col-reverse gap-[1.5rem] md:grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] md:gap-[2.75rem]"
      >
         <section class="md:order-2">
            <div
               class="relative flex h-full max-h-[45rem] min-h-[25.375rem] w-full flex-col items-end justify-between rounded-3xl lg:min-h-[30.375rem] 2xl:min-h-[40.375rem]"
               style={{
                  background: `linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)), url('/images/about/hero.jpg')`,
                  backgroundSize: "cover",
                  backgroundPosition: "center",
               }}
            >
            </div>
         </section>
         <div class="flex flex-grow flex-col justify-center gap-6 2xl:gap-8">
            <p
               class="w-fit rounded-full bg-primary-1/5 p-4 px-6 text-lg font-[900] text-primary-1 md:p-4 md:px-8 md:text-2xl"
            >
               Our Story
            </p>

            <p class="text-[1.18rem] leading-[2.4rem] tracking-[0.0225rem] text-gray-500">
               Founded by a team of experts passionate about construction and finance, buildCAP was
               born out of a need to address a critical challenge in the construction industry - the
               financing gap faced by subcontractors. We saw the struggles of subcontractors in
               managing their cash flows and recognized the ripple effect it had on the entire
               project chain. Hence, we developed buildCAP, a platform that not only offers
               financial solutions but also brings transparency, reliability, and collaboration to
               construction projects.
            </p>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div
         class="relative flex w-full flex-col-reverse gap-[1.5rem] md:grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] md:gap-[2.75rem]"
      >
         <section>
            <div
               class="relative flex h-full max-h-[45rem] min-h-[25.375rem] w-full flex-col items-end justify-between rounded-3xl lg:min-h-[30.375rem] 2xl:min-h-[40.375rem]"
               style={{
                  background: `linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)), url('/images/about/hero3.jpg')`,
                  backgroundSize: "cover",
                  backgroundPosition: "center",
               }}
            >
            </div>
         </section>
         <div class="flex flex-grow flex-col justify-center gap-6 2xl:gap-8">
            <p
               class="w-fit rounded-full bg-primary-1/5 p-4 px-6 text-lg font-[900] text-primary-1 md:p-4 md:px-8 md:text-2xl"
            >
               Our Vision
            </p>

            <p class="text-[1.18rem] leading-[2.4rem] tracking-[0.0225rem] text-gray-500">
               Our vision is to become an integral part of the construction industry's growth and
               success, particularly in emerging markets. We aim to create a world where financial
               constraints are no longer a barrier to building dreams. By fostering strong
               relationships between subcontractors, main contractors, and suppliers, we envision a
               more connected, efficient, and thriving construction ecosystem.
            </p>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div
         class="relative flex w-full flex-col-reverse gap-[1.5rem] md:grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] md:gap-[2.75rem]"
      >
         <section class="md:order-2">
            <div
               class="relative flex h-full max-h-[45rem] min-h-[25.375rem] w-full flex-col items-end justify-between rounded-3xl lg:min-h-[30.375rem] 2xl:min-h-[40.375rem]"
               style={{
                  background: `linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)), url('/images/about/hero4.jpg')`,
                  backgroundSize: "cover",
                  backgroundPosition: "center",
               }}
            >
            </div>
         </section>
         <div class="flex flex-grow flex-col justify-center gap-6 2xl:gap-8">
            <p
               class="w-fit rounded-full bg-primary-1/5 p-4 px-6 text-lg font-[900] text-primary-1 md:p-4 md:px-8 md:text-2xl"
            >
               Our Values
            </p>

            <ul
               class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-[1.18rem] leading-[2.4rem] tracking-[0.0225rem] text-gray-500"
            >
               <li>
                  <strong>Integrity and Transparency:</strong><br /> We believe in honest and open
                  communication, fostering trust among all our stakeholders.
               </li>
               <li>
                  <strong>Innovation:</strong><br /> Continuously striving for creative solutions to
                  meet the evolving needs of the construction industry.
               </li>
               <li>
                  <strong>Collaboration:</strong><br /> Building strong partnerships with
                  contractors, subcontractors, and suppliers for mutual growth and success.
               </li>
               <li>
                  <strong>Commitment to Excellence:</strong><br /> Ensuring the highest standards in
                  all our services and interactions.
               </li>
               <li>
                  <strong>Empowerment:</strong><br /> Empowering our clients by providing them with
                  the tools and resources they need to succeed.
               </li>
            </ul>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div
         class="relative flex w-full flex-col-reverse gap-[1.5rem] md:grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] md:gap-[2.75rem]"
      >
         <section>
            <div
               class="relative flex h-full max-h-[45rem] min-h-[25.375rem] w-full flex-col items-end justify-between rounded-3xl lg:min-h-[30.375rem] 2xl:min-h-[40.375rem]"
               style={{
                  background: `linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)), url('/images/about/hero5.jpg')`,
                  backgroundSize: "cover",
                  backgroundPosition: "center",
               }}
            >
            </div>
         </section>
         <div class="flex flex-grow flex-col justify-center gap-6 2xl:gap-8">
            <p
               class="w-fit rounded-full bg-primary-1/5 p-4 px-6 text-lg font-[900] text-primary-1 md:p-4 md:px-8 md:text-2xl"
            >
               Our Promise
            </p>

            <p class="text-[1.18rem] leading-[2.4rem] tracking-[0.0225rem] text-gray-500">
               At buildCAP, we promise to be more than just a financial platform. We are your
               partners in construction, committed to supporting you at every step of your project.
               From financing to project management, we are here to ensure that your journey is
               smooth, successful, and sustainable.
            </p>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-grow flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6 2xl:gap-8">
         <p
            class="w-fit rounded-full bg-primary-1/5 p-4 px-6 text-lg font-[900] text-primary-1 md:p-4 md:px-8 md:text-2xl"
         >
            Join Us!
         </p>

         <p
            class="mx-auto max-w-xl text-center text-[1.48rem] leading-[2.4rem] tracking-[0.0225rem] text-gray-500"
         >
            Be a part of the buildCAP family and experience a new era of construction project
            management and financing. Let's build a better future together.
         </p>
      </div>
   </section>

   <section class="w-full px-container-base py-[2.5rem] lg:px-container-lg xl:px-container-xl">
   </section>
</Layout>
